  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This adversary wields the power of Destruction Release. When you cast a jutsu with the Fire or Lightning release keywords, you can change the damage to necrotic and add your proficiency bonus to the damage dealt. Necrotic damage you deal ignores temporary hit points and halves all damage reduction. </p><p>Additionally, any non-magical/non-chakra-enhanced objects within an area of effect of your jutsu that are not currently adorned/held, are disintegrated into nothing.</p>",
